<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2026 01:24:03 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>急性髓系白血病新“别吃我”信号被发现！</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/new-acute-myeloid-leukemia-dont-eat-me-signal-discovered</link><description>巨噬细胞就像《爱丽丝梦游仙境》中的爱丽丝一样，识别并消耗显示“吃我”表面标记的肿瘤细胞。然而，如果肿瘤细胞成功地发出“别吃我”信号，它们就可以逃避巨噬细胞的检测。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/new-acute-myeloid-leukemia-dont-eat-me-signal-discovered2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2026 01:24:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/new-acute-myeloid-leukemia-dont-eat-me-signal-discovered</guid></item><item><title>一个DNA字母可以引发完全的性别逆转</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/one-dna-letter-can-trigger-complete-sex-reversal</link><description>巴伊兰大学的研究人员发现，仅改变 DNA 中的一个字母就可以完全改变小鼠的性别发育。在新的研究中，&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/one-dna-letter-can-trigger-complete-sex-reversal.jpg" /&gt; 由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2026 01:09:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/one-dna-letter-can-trigger-complete-sex-reversal</guid></item><item><title>研究表明，人死后意识仍然存在——这意味着死亡还有隐藏的层面</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/your-consciousness-persists-after-you-die-research-suggests-meaning-there-are-hidden-layers-to-death</link><description>我们是否需要重新定义死亡的真正含义？一些专家这样认为。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/your-consciousness-persists-after-you-die-research-suggests-meaning-there-are-hidden-layers-to-death.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2026 00:54:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/your-consciousness-persists-after-you-die-research-suggests-meaning-there-are-hidden-layers-to-death</guid></item><item><title>纵向研究将联想学习的收益与流体智力的后续改进联系起来</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/longitudinal-study-links-associative-learning-gains-to-later-improvements-in-fluid-intelligence</link><description>随着孩子的成长，他们记忆联想的能力和解决新问题的能力会积极地相互增强。新的研究表明，这些核心认知技能在小学期间以双向循环的方式共同发展。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/longitudinal-study-links-associative-learning-gains-to-later-improvements-in-fluid-intelligence.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2026 00:39:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/longitudinal-study-links-associative-learning-gains-to-later-improvements-in-fluid-intelligence</guid></item><item><title>NASA 的阿耳忒弥斯二号告诉我们关于“概览效应”、月球的喜悦和敬畏</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/what-nasas-artemis-ii-tells-us-about-the-overview-effect-moon-joy-and-awe</link><description>阿耳忒弥斯二号的太空景观引发了一种特殊的敬畏。心理学家建议坚持下去&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/what-nasas-artemis-ii-tells-us-about-the-overview-effect-moon-joy-and-awe2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2026 00:24:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/what-nasas-artemis-ii-tells-us-about-the-overview-effect-moon-joy-and-awe</guid></item><item><title>引力波可能隐藏在原子发出的光中</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/gravitational-waves-may-be-hidden-in-the-light-atoms-emit</link><description>斯德哥尔摩大学博士后研究员 Navdeep Arya 表示：“我们的研究结果可能为紧凑型引力波传感开辟一条道路，其中相关的原子系综是毫米级的。” “为了评估实际可行性，需要进行彻底的噪声分析，但我们的初步估计是有希望的。” &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/gravitational-waves-may-be-hidden-in-the-light-atoms-emit.webp" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2026 00:09:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/gravitational-waves-may-be-hidden-in-the-light-atoms-emit</guid></item><item><title>过表达 Nectin-1 的去核细胞捕获 HSV-1 并促进病毒消除，用于单纯疱疹脑炎治疗</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/enucleated-cells-with-nectin-1-overexpression-capture-hsv-1-and-promote-viral-elimination-for-herpes-simplex-encephalitis-therapy</link><description>周等人。描述了一种针对单纯疱疹脑炎的抗病毒策略，该策略采用过表达 Nectin-1 的去核 MSC 作为诱饵。这种策略有效地隔离病毒并防止其在细胞内复制。最终，它们经历程序性细胞凋亡，从而促进巨噬细胞介导的清除。该策略为难治性病毒感染提供了一种治疗方法。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/enucleated-cells-with-nectin-1-overexpression-capture-hsv-1-and-promote-viral-elimination-for-herpes-simplex-encephalitis-therapy.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Apr 2026 23:54:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/enucleated-cells-with-nectin-1-overexpression-capture-hsv-1-and-promote-viral-elimination-for-herpes-simplex-encephalitis-therapy</guid></item><item><title>现代乳房放射显示心脏风险最小</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/modern-breast-radiation-shows-minimal-heart-risks</link><description>一项大型队列研究表明，现代技术大大降低了历史上与左侧乳腺癌放射治疗相关的心脏病风险。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/modern-breast-radiation-shows-minimal-heart-risks.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Apr 2026 23:39:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/modern-breast-radiation-shows-minimal-heart-risks</guid></item><item><title>镇静免疫细胞可缓解自闭症症状</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/calming-immune-cells-eases-autism-symptoms</link><description>研究人员发现，自闭症儿童体内的调节性 T 细胞数量减少且功能发生改变，从而导致炎症。在小鼠模型中，恢复这些免疫细胞可以减少炎症并改善社交行为。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/calming-immune-cells-eases-autism-symptoms.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Apr 2026 23:24:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/calming-immune-cells-eases-autism-symptoms</guid></item><item><title>用于热机械耦合下橡胶隔振器疲劳寿命预测的物理信息 LSTM</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/physics-informed-lstm-for-fatigue-life-prediction-of-rubber-isolators-under-thermo-mechanical-coupling</link><description>橡胶支撑在汽车、重型机械和航空航天工程中至关重要。它们具有出色的超弹性、粘弹性耗散和降噪功能。然而，它们在热机械耦合载荷下的疲劳演变异常复杂。本研究开发了一个 LSTM-Physics-Informed Neural Network (PINN) 框架，它将先前的物理知识迁移与偏微分方程 (PDE) 约束相结合，以解决预测热机械损伤耦合下橡胶隔振器疲劳寿命的挑战。&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Apr 2026 23:09:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/physics-informed-lstm-for-fatigue-life-prediction-of-rubber-isolators-under-thermo-mechanical-coupling</guid></item></channel></rss>